snippet.title: Super PickUps - PlayStation 2 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Published by XS Games, this was one of the earlier titles from Milestone S.r.l., the studio best known for Hot Wheels: Unleashed, Monster Energy Supercross and RIDE series.

Race faster and wilder than ever with super modified racing pickups! Increase your racing skills and compete in challenging race circuits to win big cash prizes. Use your winnings to customize your racing pickup to dominate the race and take 1st place!

Super PickUps (C) XS Games LLC
Also available on Nintendo Wii
